CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 26, 1956, pg. 3, reads: " "Look A There" - The novel sight of a horse-drawn wagon on Centre Ave., temporarily interrupted the pretzel-eating of these two cute youngsters. Lavita Williams, left, seated on steps in 2500 block of Centre Ave, saw the horse and wagon first, and pointed it out to her friend, Vonda McCray. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Lavita Williams, and Vonda McCray, holding pretzels, seated on porch step of brick house on 2500 block of Centre Avenue, Hill District
